The paper presents a machine learning approach for breast tumor classification based on microarray gene expression data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and bioinformatics (cs.BIO).
